<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>

<section xml:id="Grading">

  <title>MATH 123 Quiz Demo</title>
  
   <subsection>
      <title>Problem 1</title>

      <p>
        Convert the following quadratic function to vertex form (<m> f(x)=a(x-h)^2+k  </m>).  State the vertex.  Further, state the domain and range.  

        <me> f(x)=x^2+12x-15</me>
      </p>
    

    </subsection>

    <subsection>
    <title>Problem 2</title>

      <p>
        Solve the following system of equations.  
        <md>
          <mrow>\frac{1}{2}x+\frac{1}{3}y \amp = \frac{1}{3}</mrow>
          <mrow>\frac{3}{2}x+\frac{1}{4}y \amp = -\frac{1}{8}</mrow>
        </md>
      </p>
    </subsection>


