  <subsection>
    <title>Problem 4</title>
    <p> Sketch a graph of the following piecewise function. 
      <me>
      f(x) = \begin{cases}
        5x \amp x\le 0 \\
        3 \amp 0\leq x \leq 2 \\
        x^2 \amp x \ge 2 \\
      \end{cases}
      </me>
      </p>
    </subsection>

